The method for predicting electric consumptions is characterized in that it comprises the following steps: 
- selecting input data; 
- pre-processing the data; 
- configuring the settings of an ANFIS, from an input data selection, the number of membership functions, the type of input membership functions and/or the type of output membership functions; 
- training of the ANFIS; and 
- evaluation of the ANFIS.  Preferably, the ANFIS is an adaptative network based on a Takagi-Sugeno fuzzy system.
